How to run the AI tutor:
1. Download openai, python-dotenv, and Streamlit by typint he folowing into your terminal:
  pip install openai
  pip install python-dotenv
  pip install streamlit
2. Get a secret key from openai's API website by going to: https://platform.openai.com/settings/organization/api-keys. Create and copy a secret key, then paste it into
the .env file in this repository where it says [YOUR SECRET KEY]. 
3. Make sure you have AI_Tutor.py and .env in the same folder. Then go to the terminal and cd to the folder where AI_Tutor.py and .env are located. Type into your terimal:
  Streamlit run AI_Tutor.py
4. Your browser will open up a tab where you can use and interact with the AI tutor. 
